WebDriverWait wait
=============================================================================================================
WebDriverWait wait = new WebDriverWait(driver, Long.valueOf("2"));         // original
WebDriverWait wait = new WebDriverWait(driver, Duration.ofSeconds(2));     // worked for me

WebDriverWait wait = new WebDriverWait(Driver.getDriver(), timeout);      //  original  , timeout is int.
WebDriverWait wait = new WebDriverWait(driver, Duration.ofSeconds(timeout));     // worked for me

